short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Inject new code into Las Positas Class-Web

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Improves Las Positas Class-Web site
- Improved Styling and Visibility!
- Dark mode!
- Navbar shows things that students actually want to see!
- Log out actually logs you out!
- You can add classes to google calendar!
- You can see where your classes are on a map to find them in person easily!
- You can see your teachers ratings on rate my professor!
